Motorcycle thefts in Czechia

czechia_mcycle_thefts.Rd

Dataset of 9,464 thefts of two-wheeled motor vehicles in Czechia between 2020 and 2022.

Usage

czechia_mcycle_thefts

Format

An SF object containing 9,464 rows and 3 columns:

id

Incident number

date

Date-time of incident

geometry

SF point geometry

This dataset is also available as a stand-alone file in geo-package format at https://mpjashby.github.io/crimemappingdata/czechia_mcycle_thefts.gpkg.

Licence: Bespoke licence, see https://kriminalita.policie.cz/

Source

Police of the Czech Republic https://kriminalita.policie.cz/
